@10011 =  ~Lord Leoncourt's treasure chest.

A strange creature, half-rabbit, half-demon by the name of Lepus, with an uncanny liking for pants, was lurking with the chest in the ritual chamber. We defeated it, and Arudin teleported us back to Athkatla. Lord Leoncourt is awaiting for us all in the Copper Coronet, and the Dungeon Crawlers have already headed there.~
@10012 =  ~Lord Leoncourt's treasure chest.

Lord Leoncourt was very pleased to get his favourite pants back, and we received our reward: ten thousand gold, to be split equally between me and Durnkrag's band. This adventure is finally over.~